room_title: Escape room "Darklight" by Outside the Box in Webster
room_description:
Take on your friends in a head-to-head puzzle battle against the clock.  Two teams. Two identical rooms with identical puzzles. Most points after 60 minutes wins.

But that's not it...

Each puzzle has a unique piece that only ONE team can get. SO... sabotage is encouraged! Take their pieces, take their points, or plunge them into utter darkness.  (or make them dress up in a costume and dance like their life depends on itâ€¦ever seen grandpa twerk? We have!).

Hopefully they won't hate you for too long...
